#include<stdio.h>
#include<iostream>
#include<map>
using namespace std;
map<string,int> map1;
int main()
{
    int i,j,k,l,t;
    //JAN, FEB, MAR, APR, MAY, JUN, JUL, AUG, SEP, OCT, NOV, DEC.
    map1["JAN"]=1;
    map1["FEB"]=2;
    map1["MAR"]=3;
    map1["APR"]=4;
    map1["MAY"]=5;map1["JUN"]=6;map1["JUL"]=7;map1["AUG"]=8;map1["SEP"]=9;map1["OCT"]=10;map1["NOV"]=11;map1["DEC"]=12;
    int arr[13]={0,0,31,59,90,120,151,181,212,243,273,304,334};
    scanf("%d",&t);
    k=1;
    while(t--)
    {
        char c[12];
        scanf("%s",c);
        string s="";
        j=(c[0]-48)*10+(c[1]-48);
        for(i=3;i<6;i++)
            s+=c[i];
        l=arr[map1[s]]+j;
        int z=(c[7]-48)*1000+(c[8]-48)*100+(c[9]-48)*10+(c[10]-48);
        if(z%400==0||(z%100!=0&&z%4==0))
        {
            if(s!="JAN"&&s!="FEB")
                l++;
        }
        printf("Case %d: ",k);
        if(l<=300)
            printf("%d Hundreds\n",l);
        else if(l>300&&l<=360)
            printf("%d Tens\n",l-300);
        else
            printf("%d Ones\n",l-360);
        k++;
    }
}
